public URL getBaseUrl()
Gets the Fedora base url, e.g. "http://example.org:8080/fedora". The url never includes a trailing slash.

setBaseUrl

public void setBaseUrl(URL baseUrl)
Sets the Fedora base url, e.g. "http://example.org:8080/fedora". Any trailing slash will be removed (e.g. "http://example.org/fedora/" will be replaced with "http://example.org/fedora").
